{"tid":2289283,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"11銀行離岸開戶 僅滙豐收費","createTime":"2020-11-17T07:05:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T07:08:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a1e5e52f1691e6ee0ac995515ad7ea60375330aa","tid":2289283,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T07:05:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201117/7FZ3U2GQEFGNNKLG2YATHWROV4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201117%2F7FZ3U2GQEFGNNKLG2YATHWROV4%2F&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM44c%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=e5262528\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201117%2F7FZ3U2GQEFGNNKLG2YATHWROV4%2F&h=2d41996b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201117/7FZ3U2GQEFGNNKLG2YATHWROV4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n11銀行離岸開戶 僅滙豐收費<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vuDHE-E7BYDSFK1vxIxntQmKmDU=/5244x3521/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CB2CDOL43NA4JGE4ENTI4YUDBU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FvuDHE-E7BYDSFK1vxIxntQmKmDU%3D%2F5244x3521%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCB2CDOL43NA4JGE4ENTI4YUDBU.jpg&h=3ece9bd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■以在新加坡開設離岸戶口為例，滙豐銀行不設最低要求。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】不少港人近年因應移民或到海外升學等需要，開設離岸或內地戶口，以安排資金。消委會檢視11間本地銀行相關服務，發現在開戶年齡、資產結餘及費用等各有不同。以在新加坡開設離岸戶口為例，滙豐銀行不設最低要求，花旗銀行則要求客戶相關銀行資產結餘須達150萬元，各銀行開戶手續需時亦由5至20個工作天不等，六間銀行更視乎開戶地，要求申請人須到當地確認或啟動賬戶。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：兩款嬰兒意粉含可致癌物  卡夫 Papa Alfredo 嘔吐毒素最勁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n花旗要求資產達150萬<br />\n<br />\n消委會綜合該11間有提供離岸或內地戶口服務的銀行，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n至於開戶所需時間，。。。。。。。。<br />\n。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：全部樣本有蟲碎 日清超標1.4倍<br />\n<br />\n開戶費用方面，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n除花旗銀行外，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n消委會提醒有意在外地開戶的人士，須了解需要及開戶目的，比較各銀行對資產結餘的要求、行政費以至當地滙率稅制、對銀行業監管及保障的制度，以確保得到最佳保障。"},{"pid":"0d9671d18164b0226cd53fdf884fb7a602adea7d","tid":2289283,"uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T07:08:24.000Z","msg":"消委員會琴日公佈左個詳細list 比較11間銀行離岸服務，有興趣去搵搵<br />\n<br />\nbtw , 開戶基數多到要消委員開file <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"0d9671d18164b0226cd53fdf884fb7a602adea7d","tid":2289283,"uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T07:08:24.000Z","msg":"消委員會琴日公佈左個詳細list 比較11間銀行離岸服務，有興趣去搵搵<br />\n<br />\nbtw , 開戶基數多到要消委員開file <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}